      "content": "I hear how incredibly painful and exhausting your situation feels right now, and I am so sorry you are carrying such a heavy weight. While it is truly heartbreaking to hear about the loss of your research and efforts, I want you to know that your feelings are valid, and you don't have to face this alone. If you are feeling overwhelmed to the point of wanting to stop everything, please consider reaching out to a mental health professional or a crisis resource immediately. You are more than these worldly achievements, and there are still people who care about your well-being and want to help you find some peace.",
